Subject: [PATCH AUTOSEL 5.2 59/59] tpm: tpm_ibm_vtpm: Fix unallocated banks
Date:   Tue,  6 Aug 2019 17:33:19 -0400
Message-Id: <20190806213319.19203-59-sashal@kernel.org>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.20.1
